.TH "ti_bandgap_force_single_read" 9 "ti_bandgap_force_single_read" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
ti_bandgap_force_single_read \- executes 1 single ADC conversion
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" ti_bandgap_force_single_read
.BI "(struct ti_bandgap *bgp "  ","
.BI "int id "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "bgp" 12
pointer to struct ti_bandgap
.IP "id" 12
sensor id which it is desired to read 1 temperature
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Used to initialize the conversion state machine and set it to a valid
state. Called during device initialization and context restore events.
.SH "RETURN"
0
